<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="thin-adj">thin <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /θɪn/    美 /θɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-thick-fat">1.★ <strong>薄的；细的 反 thick；瘦的 反 fat：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a thin blouse
薄薄的女衬衫</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a thin stick / line
细棍/线</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>thin arms / fingers
纤细的胳膊/手指</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>稀疏的；淡的；稀薄的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a thin audience in the hall
礼堂中寥寥无几的观众</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>thin blue
淡蓝</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>thin air
稀薄的空气</p></div></div>